Package: wagnerwhitin
Type: Package
Title: Wagner-Whitin Dynamic Lot Sizing Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Vince", "Castillo", email = "castillo.230@osu.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Wagner-Whitin algorithm for dynamic lot sizing with
    time-varying demand. Output is formatted to match the Excel-based teaching
    convention used in supply chain management courses. Also includes safety
    stock (SS), reorder point (ROP), and economic order quantity (EOQ) functions.
